{"tid":483104,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「扮靚」一詞於普通話/國語的應用","createTime":"2017-11-28T21:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T23:53:47.000Z","uid":155723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4fcf93467d7e581f72dfcc598bba0e510bd93c1a","tid":483104,"uid":155723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T21:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/050432_a7343d2567ee0e23cb3f1db22e6d1a2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F050432_a7343d2567ee0e23cb3f1db22e6d1a2b.jpg&h=fce2e951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如圖所示，照片攝於北京，扮靚這詞應該係廣東話用法，點解會用於普通話標語上？"},{"pid":"a7f3d1edc688dbb0ec8cd703d1b10ff9c4c652a2","tid":483104,"uid":155723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T21:15:09.000Z","msg":"扮字同靚字既意思粵普都一樣，但扮靚一詞我真係唔知可以用於普通話上"},{"pid":"0a2f45e1d3be8947910b3647510fd7b4729d8fa3","tid":483104,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T22:26:58.000Z","msg":"文化交流既一種體現姐，<br />\n外來用詞可以進入香港，粵詞就唔可以衝出本土嗎？<br />\n普通話美女你聽得多，可是靚女也不是鮮見。或許扮靚一詞古不限用於粵，又或者是受周星馳既配音電影影響都未定。"},{"pid":"08a5eac8337b6bccd49112fc0b162fb8a7394543","tid":483104,"uid":117821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T23:01:26.000Z","msg":"裝b"},{"pid":"7367662b468fe4356758f602711dda4aeefb14b1","tid":483104,"uid":19004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T23:53:47.000Z","msg":"裝b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}